flowchart TD
    USER[Human input]

    ROUTER{Entry router}

    DIRECT[Direct mode<br/>single controlled inquiry]
    SOP[SOP router<br/>load sop-header skill]

    GK[Gatekeeper<br/>validate operating contract]
    GK_RESULT{Gatekeeper verdict}

    LBA[Loop Brief Assistant<br/>identify missing conditions]
    HUMAN_FILL[Human supplies<br/>missing conditions]
    GK_RECHECK[Gatekeeper re-evaluation]

    REJECT[Reject / stop]
    BRIEF[Trusted Loop Brief]

    SM[Sensemaker<br/>frame problem and retrieve memory]
    PLAN[Normalized task frame<br/>criteria, risks, non-goals]

    GOV[Governor<br/>policy and authority enforcement]

    GEN[Generator / Actor<br/>produce changes or candidate result]
    INT[Integrator<br/>compose parallel outputs]
    EVAL[Evaluator<br/>verify explicit criteria]

    RESULT{Evaluation result}

    STATE[State Steward<br/>record state transition<br/>and memory proposals]
    META[Meta-Evaluator<br/>challenge frame, evidence,<br/>metrics and completion claim]

    META_RESULT{Meta verdict}

    MEM_DECISION{Accepted durable<br/>knowledge exists?}
    MC[Memory Curator<br/>produce OKF documents]
    OKF[okfctl transaction<br/>validate, index, commit]
    WIKI[(LLMWiki<br/>OKF knowledge bundle)]

    COMPLETE[Turn completed]
    REVISE[Revision required<br/>start next iteration]
    ESCALATE[Escalate to human]

    WD[Watchdog<br/>deterministic runtime monitoring]
    RECOVERY[Watchdog / Recovery<br/>continue, rollback or escalate]

    LEARN[Learning Observer<br/>cross-turn deterministic metrics]
    AUDIT[Learning Auditor<br/>interpret long-term learning health]

    TRIGGER[Scheduler / external trigger]
    NEXT[Next loop execution]

    USER --> ROUTER

    ROUTER -->|direct:| DIRECT
    ROUTER -->|header:| SOP
    ROUTER -->|normal input| GK

    GK --> GK_RESULT
    GK_RESULT -->|READY| BRIEF
    GK_RESULT -->|NEEDS_INPUT| LBA
    GK_RESULT -->|REJECT| REJECT

    LBA --> HUMAN_FILL
    HUMAN_FILL --> GK_RECHECK
    GK_RECHECK -->|READY| BRIEF
    GK_RECHECK -->|NEEDS_INPUT| REJECT
    GK_RECHECK -->|REJECT| REJECT

    BRIEF --> SM
    WIKI -. selected prior knowledge .-> SM
    SM --> PLAN

    PLAN --> GOV
    GOV -->|allowed| GEN
    GOV -->|denied| ESCALATE
    GOV -->|human approval required| ESCALATE

    GEN --> INT
    INT --> EVAL
    EVAL --> RESULT

    RESULT -->|PASS candidate| STATE
    RESULT -->|FAIL| REVISE

    STATE --> META
    META --> META_RESULT

    META_RESULT -->|PASS| MEM_DECISION
    META_RESULT -->|REVISE| REVISE
    META_RESULT -->|ESCALATE| ESCALATE

    MEM_DECISION -->|yes| MC
    MEM_DECISION -->|no| COMPLETE
    MC --> OKF
    OKF --> WIKI
    OKF --> COMPLETE

    GEN -. tool events .-> WD
    INT -. tool events .-> WD
    EVAL -. tool events .-> WD
    STATE -. tool events .-> WD
    META -. tool events .-> WD

    WD -->|healthy| COMPLETE
    WD -->|tripped| RECOVERY

    RECOVERY -->|continue with changed approach| REVISE
    RECOVERY -->|rollback| ESCALATE
    RECOVERY -->|escalate| ESCALATE

    COMPLETE --> LEARN
    LEARN --> AUDIT

    TRIGGER --> NEXT
    COMPLETE -. persisted state .-> NEXT
    WIKI -. reusable knowledge .-> NEXT
    AUDIT -. policy and process recommendations .-> NEXT
